posts.post_title: FS - T206 LOT - 57 low grade P/F/G
posts.post_content:
Hi everyone,

Here is a nice starter lot of 57 T206.  Cards range in condition from Poor to Good.  Please don't expect any to grade higher than a 2.5 or 3.
Not looking to break it up,  only sell as a lot.

Looking for $725USD net to me via PP (including delivery).

That works out to under $13 a card!!!

Cheers,

Andy
